Beauty" about Washington.

00:49:28.790 --> 00:49:33.200
Justice being social justice
mainly for the Black residents.

00:49:33.200 --> 00:49:37.580
Beauty being the monumental core,
the lovely city that really sort

00:49:37.580 --> 00:49:41.370
