the McMillan Plan in 1901.

00:49:41.370 --> 00:49:45.050
But -- and Shepherd was
hands-down, he was for beauty;

00:49:45.050 --> 00:49:47.600
he was for building the
elegant physical city.

00:49:47.600 --> 00:49:52.170
He really didn't care very much
about the issue of social justice.

00:49:52.170 --> 00:49:53.900
And I think that, and certainly

00:49:53.900 --> 00:50:00.800
in his mind beauty certainly
triumphed over justice.

00:50:00.800 --> 00:50:02.710
In any event, that's the story.

